      "text": "The clause does not specify the governing law or jurisdiction for this agreement. This creates uncertainty regarding legal recourse in case of disputes.",
      "severity": "major",
      "references": ["Governing law", "Marketing Agreement"]
    },
    {
      "text": "The clause lacks clarity on penalty provisions, including liquidated damages and potential remedies for breach of contract. This raises concerns about financial losses and potential disputes.",
      "severity": "major",
      "references": ["Penalty", "Liquidated Damages", "Marketing Agreement"]
    }
  ],
  "favoursWhom": "non-operator" 
